# AI Project Manager MCP Server Root Marker
# This file identifies the root directory of the AI Project Manager MCP server.
# It enables path resolution for templates, configuration, and resources.
# 
# Structure from this root:
# ./reference/templates/     - Template files
# ./reference/directives/    - JSON directive specifications  
# ./reference/directivesmd/  - Markdown directive documentation
# ./core/                    - Core processing modules
# ./database/                - Database schema and queries
# ./tools/                   - MCP tool implementations
# 
# This file should never be deleted or moved as it's used for path resolution.